These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: satire, martial-arts, action, crime
Color: light-blue, yellow, pink, blue
Birthday: april, january, december, september
City: new-york, san-francisco, london, venice
 1. Color:light-blue is on the right of Color:yellow##1
 2. Movie-Genre:satire is in an even position##4
 3. Birthday:april is on the left of Color:pink##1
 4. Birthday:december is on the right of Movie-Genre:crime##1
 5. Color:light-blue is on the left or right of Color:yellow##3
 6. City:new-york is on the left of Movie-Genre:martial-arts##1
 7. Birthday:january == Movie-Genre:action##1
 8. City:london is in an even position##4
 9. City:new-york is between City:venice and Color:blue##2
10. Movie-Genre:satire == City:venice##1
11. Color:pink == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre          | action  | satire    | crime    | martial-arts   |
| Color   | yellow     | light-blue   | pink       | blue    |
| Birthday   | january | april | september    | december |
| City           | san-francisco | venice       | new-york | london     |

